name: Azure-Necked Longplume Ibis
description: A stately, majestic avian with a long wingspan and azure neck.\nSince settling in the Realm Within, the plumage of the Longplume Ibis has grown increasingly lustrous. When they wheel across the sky in great flocks, their swirling formations resemble dizzying halos in motion, enough to make one's head spin...\nFor reasons unknown, some animals that enter the Realm Within retain their peculiar appearance shaped by the force of kuuvahki. To help Tubby identify them, Paimon has thoughtfully given them new names based on said appearance...
